name: Vortexer
description: Vortexer is a legendary cyberpunk distorted superbike that blurs the lines between the real and virtual worlds. With its cutting edge dimensional portal technology, it rips through dark alleys and neon-lit highways alike. Bold riders who dare take this risk reap the rewards of its radical acceleration and Quantum-Shift abilities, leaving all other bikes in its wake. This is a vehicle that will make even the toughest biker feel like they've hitched a ride on a portal to another universe.
